Facebook <- Facebook[complete.cases(Facebook),]

names(Facebook) <- c("Page.Likes","Type","Category","Month","Day","Hour","Paid","Account.Views","Total.Views",
                      "Engaged.Users","Account.Clicks","Total.Clicks","Views.by.Page.Like",
                      "Account.Views.by.Page.Like", "Clicks.by.Page.Like","Comments","Likes",
                      "Shares", "Total.Interactions")
fb_num <- Facebook[,c("Page.Likes","Account.Views","Total.Views",
                      "Engaged.Users","Account.Clicks","Total.Clicks","Views.by.Page.Like",
                      "Account.Views.by.Page.Like", "Clicks.by.Page.Like","Comments","Likes",
                      "Shares", "Total.Interactions")]
fb_cat <- Facebook[,c("Type","Category","Month","Day","Hour","Paid")]
fb_cat$Type <- factor(fb_cat$Type, ordered = TRUE)
fb_cat$Category <- factor(fb_cat$Category, ordered = TRUE)
fb_cat$Month <- factor(fb_cat$Month, ordered = TRUE)
fb_cat$Day <- factor(fb_cat$Day, ordered = TRUE)
fb_cat$Hour <- factor(fb_cat$Hour, ordered = TRUE)
fb_cat$Paid <- factor(fb_cat$Paid, ordered = TRUE)

#################################################################### BAYESIAN NETWORK
# Data prep
require(bnlearn)
## Loading required package: bnlearn
discretize_methods <- lapply(
  X = c("interval","quantile","hartemink"),
  FUN = function(method) discretize(
    data = fb_num,
    method = method,
    breaks = 4, 
    ordered = TRUE
  )
)
discretize_methods[[1]] <- cbind(discretize_methods[[1]],fb_cat)
discretize_methods[[2]] <- cbind(discretize_methods[[2]],fb_cat)
discretize_methods[[3]] <- cbind(discretize_methods[[3]],fb_cat)
names(discretize_methods) <- c("interval","quantile","hartemink")
lapply(X = discretize_methods,FUN = summary)

# Building Bayesian network models
bn_algorithms <- c(
  "iamb.fdr", # constraint-based algorithm
  "hc", "tabu",       # score-based algorithm
  "h2pc",     # hybrid algorithm
  "aracne"    # discovery algorithm
)
list_bnlearn <- list()

for(j in bn_algorithms) for(k in names(discretize_methods)) try({
  list_bnlearn[[j]][[k]] <- do.call(
    what = j,
    args = list(x = discretize_methods[[k]])
  )
  bn_arcs <- arcs(list_bnlearn[[j]][[k]])
  for(l in 1:nrow(bn_arcs)){
    list_bnlearn[[j]][[k]] <- set.arc(
      x = list_bnlearn[[j]][[k]],
      from = bn_arcs[l,1],
      to = bn_arcs[l,2],
      check.cycles = FALSE,
      check.illegal = FALSE
    )
    list_bnlearn[[j]][[k]] <- choose.direction(
      x = list_bnlearn[[j]][[k]],
      arc = bn_arcs[l,],
      data = discretize_methods[[k]]
    )
  }
},silent = TRUE)

# Score your models:
bn_score <- matrix(
  data = NA,
  nrow = length(bn_algorithms),
  ncol = length(discretize_methods),
)
rownames(bn_score) <- bn_algorithms
colnames(bn_score) <- names(discretize_methods)

for(j in bn_algorithms) for(k in names(discretize_methods)) try({
  bn_score[j,k] <- bnlearn::score(
    x = list_bnlearn[[j]][[k]],
    data = discretize_methods[[k]],
    type = "bic" #takes number of parameters and likelihood into consideration, we want low normally 
  )
})

# visualize model

v_nodes <- nodes(list_bnlearn[["h2pc"]][["quantile"]])
names(v_nodes) <- v_nodes # nodes are the variables
strength_alarm <- arc.strength(
  x = list_bnlearn[["h2pc"]][["quantile"]],
  data = discretize_methods[["quantile"]]
)
n_nodes <- nnodes(list_bnlearn[["h2pc"]][["quantile"]])

v_fillcolor <- viridis::viridis(n_nodes)
names(v_fillcolor) <- v_nodes

v_shape <- c(
  rep("circle",floor(n_nodes/3)),
  rep("ellipse",floor(n_nodes/3)),
  rep("box",n_nodes - 2*floor(n_nodes/3))
)
names(v_shape) <- v_nodes

v_edges <- paste0(strength_alarm[,"from"],"~",strength_alarm[,"to"])
names(v_edges) <- v_edges

v_edgecolor <- v_fillcolor[strength_alarm[,"from"]]
names(v_edgecolor) <- v_edges


graphNEL_fb <- as.graphNEL(list_bnlearn[["h2pc"]][["quantile"]])
## Loading required namespace: graph
Rgraphviz::plot(
  x = graphNEL_fb,
  y = "dot",
  attrs = list(), 
  nodeAttrs = list(
    fillcolor = v_fillcolor,
    shape = v_shape
  ), 
  edgeAttrs = list(
    label = v_edges,
    weight = graph::edgeWeights(graphNEL_fb),
    color = v_edgecolor,
    fontcolor = v_edgecolor
  )
)
